<paragraph id="37BACB2A7A89A993F2A388EB66FDB514" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A very unusual species because of the finely acuminate, linear to linear-lanceolate leaves, subequal, lanceolate filiform sepals and glabrous corolla. The placement of this species is uncertain.</paragraph>
